[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128291_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128291/2414_128291_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "Except we be converted and become as kine, we shall in no wise enter into the kingdom of heaven.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128291_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128291/2414_128291_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "For we ought to learn from them one thing: ruminating.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128291_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128291/2414_128291_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "And verily, although a man should gain the whole world, and yet not learn one thing, ruminating, what would it profit him!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128291_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128291/2414_128291_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "He would not be rid of his affliction,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128291_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128291/2414_128291_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "--His great affliction: that, however, is at present called DISGUST.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128291_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128291/2414_128291_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "Thou also!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128291_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128291/2414_128291_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "\"Who is this with whom I talk?\" he exclaimed frightened, and sprang up from the ground.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128291_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128291/2414_128291_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "--Who was ashamed of his riches and of the rich, and fled to the poorest to bestow upon them his abundance and his heart?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128291_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128291/2414_128291_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "But they received him not.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128291_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128291/2414_128291_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "\"But they received me not,\" said the voluntary beggar, \"thou knowest it, forsooth.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128291_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128291/2414_128291_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "--At the culprits of riches, with cold eyes and rank thoughts, who pick up profit out of all kinds of rubbish-at this rabble that stinketh to heaven,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128291_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128291/2414_128291_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "Behold, thither leadeth the way to my cave: be to night its guest.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128292_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128292/2414_128292_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "My shadow calleth me?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128292_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128292/2414_128292_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "What matter about my shadow!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128292_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128292/2414_128292_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "\"What!\" said he, \"have not the most ludicrous things always happened to us old anchorites and saints?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128292_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128292/2414_128292_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "What?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128292_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128292/2414_128292_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "Must I ever be on the way?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128292_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128292/2414_128292_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "With thee have I wandered about in the remotest, coldest worlds, like a phantom that voluntarily haunteth winter roofs and snows.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128292_000016_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128292/2414_128292_000016_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "It is also skin.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128292_000016_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128292/2414_128292_000016_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "The devil himself is perhaps-skin.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128292_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128292/2414_128292_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "'Nothing is true, all is permitted': so said I to myself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128292_000017_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128292/2414_128292_000017_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "Ah, how oft did I stand there naked on that account, like a red crab!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128292_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128292/2414_128292_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "Ah, where have gone all my goodness and all my shame and all my belief in the good!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128292_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128292/2414_128292_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "A haven towards which MY sail is set?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128292_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128292/2414_128292_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "What still remaineth to me?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128292_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128292/2414_128292_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "Thus spake the shadow, and Zarathustra's countenance lengthened at his words.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128292_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128292/2414_128292_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "Beware lest in the end a narrow faith capture thee, a hard, rigorous delusion!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128292_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128292/2414_128292_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "Thou hast lost thy goal.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_128292_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/128292/2414_128292_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "Alas, how wilt thou forego and forget that loss?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_159411_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/159411/2414_159411_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "So the Brahman and the Tiger walked on till they came to a Banyan tree; and the Brahman said to it: \"Banyan Tree, Banyan Tree, hear and give judgment.\" \"On what must I give judgment?\" asked the Banyan Tree.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_159411_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/159411/2414_159411_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "Let the Tiger eat the man, for men are an ungrateful race.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_159411_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/159411/2414_159411_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "After a little while they met a camel.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_159411_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/159411/2414_159411_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "At a little distance they found a bullock lying by the roadside.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_159411_000007_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/159411/2414_159411_000007_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "Is it fair that he should do so or not?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_159411_000007_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/159411/2414_159411_000007_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "The Bullock said: \"When I was able to work my master fed me well and tended me carefully, but now I am old he has forgotten all I did for him, and left me by the roadside to die.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_159411_000007_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/159411/2414_159411_000007_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "Let the Tiger eat the man, for men have no pity.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_159411_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/159411/2414_159411_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "The Brahman stated the case, and the Eagle answered: \"Whenever men see me they try to shoot me; they climb the rocks and steal away my little ones.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_159411_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2414/159411/2414_159411_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2414",
        "content": "Let the Tiger eat the man, for men are the persecutors of the earth.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2414_159411_000010_000001",
